OL,3,CFlooding closes road where elderly
OL,4,Ccouple drowned in their car
OL,6,FA stretch of road where an elderly
OL,7,Fcouple drowned after their car became
OL,8,Fsubmerged in floodwater has been
OL,9,Fforced to close again in heavy rain.
OL,11,FElaine and Philip Marco, aged 75 and
OL,12,F77, died in the incident on Queens
OL,13,FDrive in Mossley Hill, Liverpool, on
OL,14,F26 August 2023.
OL,16,FThe road, a busy thoroughfare in the
OL,17,Fcity, was closed to traffic while
OL,18,Frepairs and investigations were
OL,19,Fcarried out.
