OL,3,CFlooding closes road where elderly
OL,4,Ccouple drowned in their car
OL,6,FA series of upgrades were installed
OL,7,Faround the road including barriers and
OL,8,Fflood sensors. The road was reopened
OL,9,Fin February 2024.
OL,11,FHowever, after a heavy downpour in the
OL,12,Fevening of Tuesday 9 July, the sensors
OL,13,Factivated to warn motorists and
OL,14,Fpedestrians of flooding under the
OL,15,Fbridge.
OL,17,FBarricades were put across the top of
OL,18,Fthe road preventing drivers from
OL,19,Faccessing it.
