OL,3,CFlooding closes road where elderly
OL,4,Ccouple drowned in their car
OL,6,FLiverpool City Council said that
OL,7,FQueens Drive had been closed after the
OL,8,Fflood system "successfully detected
OL,9,Frising water levels following last
OL,10,Fnight's heavy downpour, and activated
OL,11,Fthe barriers to keep people safe".
OL,13,FA council spokesperson added
OL,14,Fdiversions had been put in place.
OL,16,FThe Marcos were well-respected members
OL,17,Fof the city's Jewish community and
OL,18,Fwere described as a "quiet and humble
OL,19,Fcouple" who were "very dedicated and
OL,20,Fdevoted grandparents."
