OL,3,CFlooding closes road where elderly
OL,4,Ccouple drowned in their car
OL,6,FThe tragedy occurred just five days
OL,7,Fbefore they were due to celebrate
OL,8,Ftheir 54th wedding anniversary.
OL,10,FA statement from the couple's family
OL,11,Fsaid at the time: "We are devastated
OL,12,Fand heartbroken by the sudden loss of
OL,13,FElaine and Philip Marco. They were
OL,14,Fmuch loved parents to four children
OL,15,Fand 10 grandchildren.
