OL,3,CFlooding closes road where elderly
OL,4,Ccouple drowned in their car
OL,6,F"The family are arriving overseas from
OL,7,FAmerica and Australia to mourn their
OL,8,Floss. They were due to celebrate their
OL,9,F54th wedding anniversary next week and
OL,10,Four only comfort is knowing that they
OL,11,Fwere together to the very end."
OL,13,FIn response to the couple's death,
OL,14,FLiverpool Council oversaw a period of
OL,15,Fwork on Queens Drive, including
OL,16,Freplacement of gullies, repairs to the
OL,17,Fcarriageway including pothole
OL,18,Fmaintenance and upgraded street
OL,19,Flighting.
